<br>
to me, the problem with the high end game of everquest is the lack of opportunities for all guilds and all high end players to go after all mobs in the game.  this is the key thought process through all my posts.... high end players lacking OPPORTUNITIES.  as it stands now, the only high end players that are able to go after all that everquest has to offer is those players in the largest guilds on each server... the guilds that are able to assemble immediately after a patch and go after all the highly contested spawns on the server and succeed.  <br>
<br>
